wiki_detail.notes:
* The goo missile has a fixed travel time but is independent from when the zone is established. The puddle is destructible by effects such as {{ai|Wind Wall|Yasuo}}. The missile will also destroy {{ai|Void Shift|Malzihar}}
* ''Mega Adhesive's'' {{tip|slow}} and {{tip|ground}} debuffs are each marked as non-dispellable, so they are not removed by most {{tip|cleanse|cleanses}}. Each is however allowed to be removed by cleanses that '''also''' grant immunity to the debuff type, such as {{cai|Ragnarok|Olaf}}.
* '''Singed''' {{tip|sight|reveals}} himself to enemies briefly on-cast from fog of war if enemy targets are in the target area of ''Mega Adhesive''.{{bug|2}}
